                     <interp inst="t18630202-330-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, Stealing a handkerchief, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18630202-name-274" type="victimName">
